HEADWORD: Handsomeness
<hw>Hand"some*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality of being
handsome.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Handsomeness</qex> is the mere animal excellence, beauty the
mere imaginative.</q> <rj><qau>Hare.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

